  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are about 25<span>m²</span> and sleep up to two adults, with space for a baby cot (available on request, payable locally). The rooms are modern, fresh and functional, decorated in light tones of white and cream. The rooms are all sound proofed and have a king size bed, so you can be sure of a peaceful night sleep. Other facilities include complementary WiFi, TV with Sky channels, tea and coffee making facilities, mini bar and phone.</p>
<p>Standard rooms for single use and rooms that sleep up to three or four people are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
